{"tid":1677080,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[南亞we connect] Happy Diwali!","createTime":"2019-10-26T23:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T04:30:11.000Z","uid":89046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3427a6e611e39de2a64af4301d7c99ef46c9dfd7","tid":1677080,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T23:53:23.000Z","msg":"今日是Diwali (也叫 Deepavali)，是印度教 (Hindu)、耆那教 (Jain)、錫克教 (Sikh) 和佛教節日，中文叫「排撜節」、「光明節」或「屠妖節」，<strong>它象徵著光明壓倒黑暗和無明，正義戰勝邪惡 和不義。標示著人類文明對正義和光明的祈盼和肯定。</strong><br />\n<br />\n話說，印度人的神終於在斯里蘭卡戰勝了十頭妖魔，而就在Diwali這一天回到了印度。全城的百姓為了歡迎他們偉大的神的歸來，於是家家戶戶點起了燈籠，大家歡天喜地，慶祝神的勝利，因此這一天，也象徵光明終於戰勝黑暗、正義戰勝邪惡。<br />\n<br />\n在 Diwali當日，很多人會穿上新衣服、齊享糖果和爆竹。印度北部的商家一般都以Diwali作為財政新年度的首天，當天會用新賬簿作業。大部分的公司行號會致贈員工、客戶、往來企業各項禮品，甚至有些公司會發給禮金，就像我們在過農曆新年一樣。而很多的祝賀詞都會祝福大家有個新的一年（但不是Happy New Year而是Happy Diwali）。<br />\n<br />\n有些地方，人們一大早就會開始在地上作畫，這是一種很神奇的畫法，地上那些圖案全部都是用色粉構成的，作畫的人會很靈巧的將色粉平均撒上去，最後形成一幅美麗的圖畫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gz9s0Lx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGz9s0Lx.jpg&h=30c13322&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就連商店都會裝飾一下來慶祝！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZW7gp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZW7gp5.jpg&h=4cdfc2d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到了晚上像是一些社區就來個慶祝晚會！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpzTWiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpzTWiS.jpg&h=5a14e540&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrc2PMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyrc2PMe.png&h=97bab9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0576e03888b0322b7a01be0b76b9bd044e71d480","tid":1677080,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T00:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7fe4b78e1c09563141858c356a08a96d3c3ca4","tid":1677080,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e8c519a80f721bb82e94ff133b225be05ddf92","tid":1677080,"uid":34342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"Happy Diwali. Thx for ur hospitality last Friday."},{"pid":"3dfb848ad5049adebbb46fbe892fa1860a255a45","tid":1677080,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>主線速遞</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 10 &middot; 27 </span><br />\n追究警暴 守護民眾記者 守護穆斯林</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 10 &middot; 27</span><br />\n自由之鶴追悼會</strong></span><br />\n- 16:00 - 20:00 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">下星期六 11 &middot; 2 </span><br />\n求援國際 堅守自治</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 維園流水式集會<br />\n<br />\n詳情參閱：<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=bb3a8309\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a>"},{"pid":"d9fa03502d9b4edbbe4db4f7be168c6ab800ebe4","tid":1677080,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:30:11.000Z","msg":"提醒返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 印度教同伊斯蘭教係兩回事"}]}